  "",
  "This group extracts and hardens external runtime dependency handling. [#180](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529-safe-app/pull/180) adds `src/config/runtimeConfig.ts` as the single typed owner for browser runtime config parsing: 6529 API base URL, Safe Transaction Service base URL, mainnet RPC URL, Safe parent-origin allowlist, Safe downgrade-policy address allowlists, and build provenance metadata. Existing API clients, Safe Transaction Service helpers, runtime policy, and Safe provider code are routed through those helpers while keeping compatibility wrappers.",
