  "[#235](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/235)-[#242](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/242) repeat the same pattern for alert delivery. [#235](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/235) adds `alerts:delivery-plan`, a dry-run handoff for webhook/SNS/SES alert routing that does not send alerts, create topics, verify SES identities, call webhooks, call AWS, or read live ledgers. [#238](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/238)-[#240](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/240) gate alert delivery on cutover, operator evidence, and v0 alerts readiness.",
