  "[#281](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/281)-[#291](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/291) require release evidence for container publishing, worker dispatch credentials, public dashboard disclosure, admin dashboard auth, runtime dispatch, runtime release notes, and refresh evidence coverage roadmap docs. [#292](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/292)-[#294](https://github.com/6529-Collections/6529reviewbot/pull/294) make release tag planning check the remote, not just local tags, and add fixture coverage.",
